items.content_text:
### Dependency Injection

*   [Locatable (⭐119)](https://github.com/vincent-pradeilles/locatable) - A micro-framework that leverages Property Wrappers to implement the Service Locator pattern.

### Messaging Protocol / Barcode

*   [CocoaMQTT (⭐1.7k)](https://github.com/emqx/CocoaMQTT) - MQTT for iOS and OS X.

### Text / Barcode

*   [Tagging (⭐123)](https://github.com/k-lpmg/Tagging) - A TextView that provides easy to use tagging feature for Mention or Hashtag.

### Transition / Barcode

*   [SamuraiTransition (⭐282)](https://github.com/hachinobu/SamuraiTransition) - Swift based library providing a collection of ViewController transitions featuring a number of neat cutting animations.
